# 曾永華 教授

- Email：tzengyo@mail.ncku.edu.tw
- 個人網頁：<{{ page.profile }}>
- 實驗室組別：微電子組
- 實驗室：[{{ page.lab }}](https://www.ee.ncku.edu.tw/teacher/index2.php?teacher_id=11)
- 採訪者：{{ page.author }}
- 訪談日期：2022/11/10

### 可以請您簡單介紹實驗室的研究領域嗎？目前有在進行什麼樣的研究呢？
My laboratory is currently doing research related to the following four funded projects：
A.  Research and Development on High-performance Silicon-based Porous Anode for Lithium Ion Battery. NSTC, Taiwan
B.  Research on large-area crystalline diamond wafers and hybrid diamond-compound-semiconductor wafers – KINIK, Inc., Taiwan.
C.  Feasibility study of diamond as a thermal conductor for GaN power devices. Win Semiconductor, Taiwan.
D.  BEOL compatible diamond process for thermal and mechanical management. TSMC, Taiwan.

### 請問教授希望自己的專題生具備什麼特質或能力？
Enthusiasm  in research and curiosity in new science and technology. 

### 請問老師對於專題生有什麼樣的期望嗎？
Highly motivated for significant achievement.

### 請問老師實驗室每年大概會收多少專題生
One or two.

### 請問教授會指定研究主題嗎？或者是可以讓專題生自行指定？會安排專題生做什麼樣的學習（比如讀paper等）？專題生有機會參與實驗室正在進行的研究嗎？
all options are open for consideration.

### 請問待在教授實驗室的大學部學生一週大約得花多少時間在專題研究上？
At least ten hours

### 實驗室氣氛如何?  
Vibrant.

### 請問教授覺得為甚麼專題對於電機系的學生是重要的?
Student will Know how to put knowledge into work on significant subjects effectively.  

### 請問教授對於還沒非常了解自己興趣的同學在選擇實驗室有什麼建議？
Be proactive and study faculty information  in the Departmental website to find a best fit.

### 如果有同學成為專題生之後發現研究主題與自己興趣不合時，該怎麼辦呢？ 
Study harder and understand the subject in more depth to gain interest. 

### 老師在帶專題的過程中有沒有什麼趣事想跟系上的同學分享？
Most students continued for graduate study in my lab and then worked for top semiconductor companies after graduation.
